	</p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p style="text-align: justify">The Agreement between the Government of the Philippines and the International Center for Living Aquatic Resources Management to Establish the Office of the WorldFish Center in the Philippines (ICLARM) 
	</p>
	</li>
	<li>
